[Day 2] (event) Day 2. The quarry to the north has opened a new fissure. The workers refuse to return.
[Day 3] (omen) Day 3. The boundary thins (1% pressure). The shadows in the old quarter have been falling at the wrong angle since nightfall.
[Day 4] (faction) The Iron Mere — A procedural dispute has become a constitutional crisis.
[Day 4] (faction) The Iron Mere. The network has been repaired. They are watching again.
[Day 7] (event) Day 7. A toll has appeared on the northern pass. No one authorized it.
[Day 9] (event) Day 9. Armed groups are moving through the lowlands. They are not soldiers. They are organized.
[Day 11] (conflict) Day 11. a border engagement broke out between Drevurreach and Ashunreach. Drevurreach held. The rite was completed in the aftermath. They retreat deeper and regroup.
[Day 16] (named_entity) Day 16. From within Shanumfen, Ashan has risen. They seized the archive and declared themselves its sole interpreter. Their tenet: "To lose knowledge is to die twice.". They will not be easily forgotten.
